messageBody:
Thanks, Paul! After reading the document, I'm persuaded that these names are better than the original.

Ted

>
>
> I'm not familiar with "Zuk's renaming of the letters". Is this in any of

>
> Ted
>

Yes. Go to the files section, then to resources, then open up the file
Second Shaw.

Paul
